txt.en: Bring the spider ichor to Kavíra in Jadambor
You have gathered spider ichor from the spiders in the area. Kavíra, the healer in Jadambor would have use of these.
Spiders can be found near Jalkhûl to the south-east of Jadambor.\n\nCollect ichor and bring it to Kavíra in Jadambor.
Collect spider ichor south-east of Jadambor ([placeholder]/[placeholder])
Bring the spider ichor to Kavíra in Jadambor in western Dil-irmíz.

You hand Kavíra the spider ichor you have collected.

'My gratitude knows no bounds, [placeholder]. We are always in need of antidotes with the amount of spiders in the area so these are truly a welcomed sight. Take this for the help you have provided.

'If you happen upon any more I will be glad to take them off your hands.'

The spiders in the area have valuable ichor. Bring some to Kavíra, the healer in Jadambor, to help restock her supply for medicines.
Spiders can be found in the southern edge of Dil-irmíz. Their ichor would surely help Kavíra, the healer in Jadambor, with their medicines.
